message.body: Well, it's done.
i was at trivia!!! do you want me to call you back?
Nah. I'm so tired, I'm going right to bed. We can talk tomorrow. :)
sleep good! tty tomorrow for sure.
So. Things actually went really well last night.
how so?
We agreed that we had different goals out of life, so it's best if we went separate ways. But, we still want to be close. So he's still coming to the party
Friday. We have so many mutual friends as stuff, it's silly to mess that up.
oh, awesome! i'm really glad to hear that.
Yeah. And I'm sad, but I'm also not, because nothing is really changing. I'm working all the time, so I'll just keep doing that and I'll have way more freedom
to actually date when I move out.
that's great! it seems like friends might be more suited to what you're feeling anyway?
Yeah. And I'm not looking to rush into any more relationships. So I'm just gonna relax and have som fun for a while.
just make sure you're being safe! ;) emotionally and physically.
also we should celebrate by exploring that possible headshop and having lunch.
celebrating your breakup and your birthday, i mean. :)
I'm heading to work now. I'll let you know what days ill be free to do that :)
haha, yeah, that's what i meant. have a good day at work! love youuu.
Love youuuuu.
Lunch Friday afternoon, then Mackenzie's that night? Sound like a plan?
yeah girlll
